# Lab 02 — Fine-Tuning FLAN-T5 with PEFT/LoRA
-------------------------------------------------------
## Overview

This lab focuses on fine-tuning a language model for dialogue summarization using FLAN-T5 and the DialogSum dataset.

The main goal was to understand how model performance changes after fine-tuning and how Parameter Efficient Fine-Tuning methods such as LoRA can reduce the number of trainable parameters.
